import tensorflow as tf
from tensorflow.core.framework import tensor_pb2
from tensorflow.python.framework import dtypes

expected_tensor = tensor_pb2.TensorProto(dtype=dtypes.uint32.as_datatype_enum, uint32_val=[1,2,3,4])
expected_array = tf.make_ndarray(expected_tensor)
